item.description:
Entrepreneurs sharing great ideas - that's what we're all about. This is NOT a venue for job seekers, self-promotion networkers, commissioned sales reps that are not independent business owners, get rich quick or Multi Level Marketers.

We're a small group of business owners (and sometimes busniness owner wannabes) sharing ideas on how to profitably run and grow a business. Rather than sit back and wait for referrals we will discuss what actions we can take to build relationships with other business owners and strengthen our professional image.

Meeting attendance via RSVP only.  No fee to attend.
item.how_to_find_us: 1st floor office. No need to feed the meter - parking is free after 5 pm.
item.why: Learn at least 7 marketing techniques to propel your business. FREE to attend. Bring a colleague to enhance the interaction. New location, new format. All attendees receive a 25% off coupon toward a custom landing page to market their business.
item.name: Spring Forward! Grow Your Business with Unique Online Marketing Techniques
